<title>Kumthak Nino Hungsuok</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kum lui mangta ni leh tha kum kihei ta,
 Tuzing kumthak ni no a hungsuok;
 Khum zawl apat hungtho dawkun taisieu in,
 Kipak in lawm hitiu, ni no hungsuok hi.

[V2]
 Hung un, hung un, Lalpa chawian hitiu.
 A lungsiet hengilh ding kuo ahim?
 Kum tunga damtaka ei vengpa ahi,
 Kumsawt kumsawt in Amin lopi zing hen.

[V3]
 2. Hinkhuo tawpa chieh masa I ngaih teu chu,
 Tuni'n van gam nuomah a leng ui;
 Bang di'n lei ah amau puldo ding I him?
 Kum tunga ei vengpa Pathien chawian un.

[V4]
 3. Kipahna thu leh sepgah chawiin hung un,
 Tuni'n Pathien a hung vang pie di'n:
 Hukdampa'n na chanchin na phuon a deih hi,
 Kum tunga mawhna phuongin suol haihsan ta'n.

[V5]
 4. Kum lui thai ting kum thak lawpna'n lasai tiu,
 Na bawn un Inkuon in hungtel un;
 Dan leh Pa vangpiek na cha'nte kisik ding,
 Kipak in lawp hitiu, Pa leh Hukdam pa.</lyrics>
</song>